Package: securer
Title: Secure R Code Execution with Tool-Call IPC
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R:
    person("Posit", "PBC", email = "engineering@posit.co", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Wraps callr::r_session with a bidirectional IPC protocol for
    pause/resume tool calls, enabling safe execution of LLM-generated R code.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
